be.haraka.game4.Graphics

Class ModelList

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.haraka.game4.Graphics.Models.ModelList

  • public class ModelList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains a hashmap loaded from a JSON File. The hashmap consists of Model with String as a key and is needed to link the right model to the right GameObject from the GameObject's GameObject.objectName.
